segment.source: The About dialog boxes display information about the specific version of the Microsoft Management Console or the specific version of the Application Virtualization Desktop Client or Client for Remote Desktop Services (formerly Terminal Services) Management Console.
segment.target: The About dialog boxes display information about the specific version of the Microsoft Management Console or the specific version of the Application Virtualization Desktop Client or Client for Remote Desktop Services (formerly Terminal Services) Management Console.

segment.source: To display these dialog boxes, click Help and select About Microsoft Management Console or About Application Virtualization Client Management Console.
segment.target: To display these dialog boxes, click Help and select About Microsoft Management Console or About Application Virtualization Client Management Console.
